== CONSTANTS ==

• COS_30      - cos(30°) ≈ 0.866
• COS_30_INV  - 1/cos(30°) ≈ 1.155

== FUNCTIONS ==

• skewY(points, deg, zeroOffset)
    Vertical shear on array of Points.

• scaleX(size, factor) / scaleY(size, factor)
    Scale Size horizontally/vertically.

• getAllGraphics(graphic)
    Flatten groups into array of leaf graphics.

• applySkewY(graphic, deg)
    Vertical skew on graphic. Skips Lines.

• applyScale(graphic, axis, factor)
    Scale bounding box. axis: 'x' or 'y'

• makePlane(graphic, planeType)
    Isometric transform. planeType: 'left', 'right', 'topLeft', 'topRight'
